Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:59.95,Ryōko tl notes,Lad,0,0,0,,[Note: This is a poem by Saigyou Houshi.]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:56.09,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,I wish to die in spring, under the blossoming trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.95,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,on full moon's day during the month of February.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.32,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Dubois?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:05.64,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The Metropolitan Police Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:09.59,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,What business does the Paris district police department's perverted vice-chief of bureau have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:19.51,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,So that woman's... started to make her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.77,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Izumida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.75,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,S-Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.11,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.61,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.60,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:00.90,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:10.95,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Let us bid farewell to the pair making their way to God's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.04,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,Farewell, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.46,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,Both of you, may your days be filled with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.85,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Make sure you rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.93,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Senpai, you can leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.31,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.74,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Keep a close eye on her so she won't come back to haunt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.19,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.89,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.52,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.61,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Even Hell would feel like Heaven if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:46.66,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,No, if you're with me, even Heaven will feel like Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.08,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,That was a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.49,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,I remember dreaming the same dream about two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:56.47,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Just like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.76,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,What unpleasant mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:03.43,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,But what awaited me at the Metropolitan Police\NDepartment was completely different from a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.19,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,It was unexpectedly good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:06.72,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.61,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:14.95,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,As I said, we received a call from Superintendent Yakushiji earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:18.85,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Apparently, she won't be coming here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.70,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,It sounded like she was calling from the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.61,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.68,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,She probably went out of the country for a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.08,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,{\t(840,2383,\alpha&HFF&}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.41,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.48,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:38.32,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,It's not like we're doing this behind her back or anything, but do you guys want to go for a drink tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.89,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.88,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,In that case, there's a Cantonese\Nrestaurant that I'd like to recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.27,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Cantonese food, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.34,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,I'm not too fond of oily food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.19,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Izumida-san, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.58,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.94,Ryōko overlap,Old,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}When you get older, the oil feels heavy in your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.12,Ryōko overlap,Sat,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.87,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:58.50,Ryōko overlap,Old,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}Tonight, I think we should go somewhere cheap and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.32,Ryōko overlap,Old,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.74,Ryōko overlap,Sat,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}Yes, that sounds good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.32,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Okay, I've given it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.63,Ryōko overlap,Old,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.24,Ryōko overlap,Old,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}Leave the restaurant to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.29,Ryōko overlap,sat,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.06,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oh my, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.61,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Izumida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.40,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:40.24,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yakushiji makes me do this every time, so I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:44.47,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Those actions are unworthy of a public servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.36,Ryōko main,JUn,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.39,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Refrain from such actions in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.93,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I will keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.54,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,But since I've already brought it along, please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.79,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Just this once, as an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.71,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Coming here an hour earlier than your appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.12,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Was that Oryo's teaching too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.30,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.67,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,But thanks to that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.21,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.47,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:15.34,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,I almost said, "My eyes were treated to a feast."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.40,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Do you remember this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.17,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.05,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, during the Tokyo Nightmare case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:22.73,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.69,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.16,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,What do you mean by the Tokyo something or other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.63,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:36.00,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Actually, recently she has been giving\Nnames to the cases she's been involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.90,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,She's still a genius when it comes to thinking up strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.42,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Regarding her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.38,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,I hear she's out of the country right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.88,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:50.78,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes, my boss's whims are troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.25,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.13,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Did you want to discuss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.83,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Do you know this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.36,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:04.70,Ryōko main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.23,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,How about Oryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.65,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know unless we asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.06,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Yes, I would think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.20,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.24,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Most likely the Queen of Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.67,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Shiba... you mean {\i1}that{\i0} Shiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:24.23,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Shiba refers to the Metropolitan Police\NDepartment's government office tower in Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:28.60,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Ultra-secret departments, even those among the\NMetropolitan Police Department, have offices there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:32.38,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,It's a place even Yakushiji can't touch very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:36.06,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent Muromachi had a passing relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:39.60,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,with a man formerly stationed there, a man named Hyoudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:45.82,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,And that's why she's been secretly observing Shiba on her own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.69,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,I finally understood why Superintendent Muromachi used JACES Sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:58.15,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,a place practically owned by her archenemy, my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.94,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Investigations of the Shiba tower
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.35,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,would be partly taboo for someone working for the Metropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:08.84,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Our conversation would never leak outside if it happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:15.52,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Apparently, Shiba is controlled by a\Nmysterious woman known as the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.92,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Is that the woman in the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.73,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,I can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.48,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,But most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.09,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,I was hoping you might have some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.44,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.82,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.52,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,This isn't police work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.90,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,This is something I am doing personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:38.89,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent, do you plan to keep investigating Shiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:39.71,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:45.37,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,In that case, although I know my place, let me say one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.51,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Shiba's influence is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.73,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:56.93,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,That is why I ask that you treat your investigation with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.42,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.39,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,But you won't tell me to stop, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.50,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:08.40,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I know how to state my opinions to a stubborn superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:14.78,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I'm as stubborn as Oryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.66,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Izumida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.49,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,That perception of yours is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.37,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.62,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Correct it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.44,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,It was an inappropriate remark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.08,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh no, my mouth slipped at the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:42.07,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Man... I wonder when this'll end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:45.56,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I need to stop by the Yodozakura Hobby Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:08.96,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,Yakushiji Ryoko knows all your secrets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.21,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,With the thought of removing Yakushiji Ryoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:20.84,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,I've initiated a certain plan, for your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.43,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,No, for the future of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.81,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,First, there will be a big shift in the world of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.99,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,The beer tastes awfully good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.60,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.03,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.64,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,Izumida-san, you're getting too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.41,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've come to a place like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.05,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,since I used to always escort the superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:52.92,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,I don't know if I should pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:55.07,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110}Next is politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.18,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110}The opposition party that strongly condemns bureaucratic amakudari has,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:01.41,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110}as of this national assembly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.18,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,I would think that this is causing a fuss with the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:08.40,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Being non-career bureaucrats, it doesn't concern us... or rather, that is what I'd like to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.86,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,but that's not the case for Superintendent Yakushiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.01,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:16.84,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Why do you think that Superintendent Yakushiji has so much power?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:21.47,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,It's because she's strong, beautiful and her personality resembles that of a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:25.29,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Well there's that too, but that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:28.41,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,About 90% of the Metropolitan\NPolice Department's bureaucrats
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.99,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,go amakudari to JACES or one of its\Nassociated companies after they retire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.25,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.09,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,If they go up against Superintendent, they'll lose their jobs when they retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.98,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:45.77,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,It's because of this amakudari "bait" that Yakushiji Ryoko can do whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:51.31,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,If this bill is passed and amakudari itself is forbidden, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:55.29,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,Superintendent Yakushiji will be in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.91,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,But it probably won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.28,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.83,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,They're just the opposition party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:05.31,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,They'll probably just make a big fuss, but in the end, nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:09.33,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,Although it's a different story if the country accepts all of the opposition party's bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.79,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,It probably won't happen and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.25,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Here are your servings of Yakitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.86,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.62,Ryōko main,Old,0,0,0,,For seconds, can I have Shochu with coarse tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.89,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.63,Ryōko main,Sat,0,0,0,,I'll get a double Baigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.34,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Two coarse teas and a Baibai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.52,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.74,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,But one week later, the impossible happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:39.92,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Is Yakushiji Ryoko currently following up on the news that would endanger her position?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.28,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,Oh, what time is it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.76,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.24,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,I drank too much last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.46,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,On to the next topic:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.90,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,"The root of all evil is the beautiful, female superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.65,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,Her name is Yakushiji Ryoko."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.70,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.43,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,This is from Nitto Sports's city news section.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.85,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,In relation to the Metropolitan Police Department's amakudari problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:11.26,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,most people are interested in the most prominent amakudari destination
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:15.40,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,and Yakushiji Ryoko, the woman next-in-line at JACES.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.58,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,She's an elite police bureaucrat who graduated from Tokyo University.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:21.02,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,She's beautiful, cunning, and her father is a former Metropolitan Police Department bureaucrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.02,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,A thoroughbred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.50,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,The article also states that, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.87,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,her selfishness is also well-known within the Metropolitan Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:29.36,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,They wrote an article on Oryo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:32.62,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear anything bad about Oryo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:35.12,Ryōko italic,Ann,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}It also states that, according to witnesses,\NSuperintendent Yakushiji's selfishness was incomparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:43.07,Ryōko italic,Guy,0,0,0,,She thinks that the police organizations that exist for the country's safety belong to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:46.66,Ryōko italic,Guy,0,0,0,,Letting a woman with no respect for the country\Nwhatsoever stay in the Metropolitan Police Department is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:51.10,Ryōko italic,Guy,0,0,0,,very dangerous, even if she's in management.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.85,Ryōko italic,Guy,0,0,0,,Besides, around us are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:58.31,Ryōko italic,Lad,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}There have been numerous bureaucratic scandals in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:04.02,Ryōko italic,Lad,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}so I don't believe the citizens will be content until she provides an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:08.16,Ryōko italic,Lad,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\an8}And the government's response is nothing but poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.68,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:09.95,Ryōko main,Jac,0,0,0,,Why is every channel broadcasting something about Oryo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.37,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Things have become troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:23.43,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,We've decided to write a special article on Superintendent Yakushiji too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.17,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Even Nitto Daily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.63,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Not just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.47,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Everyone who visits the Press Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.45,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.50,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,How about it, Izumida-han?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.02,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Want to be my personal informant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.85,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.74,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.61,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's for helping me with the coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.18,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Putting aside whether Yakushiji is right or wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.69,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,it's vexing that you think I'm\Nsomeone who would sell out his boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.20,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.85,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,But if you don't treat the situation accordingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:58.68,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,you'll end up falling ill due to being\Nbashed 24/7, like some prime minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:06.59,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's great that you care for your boss, but be careful not to end up in the same coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.28,Ryōko main,Guy,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.97,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oryo is all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.74,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.48,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.46,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,It's Oryo who needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:31.59,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,But why did it turn out like this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.13,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Regarding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.71,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Shiba has made its move, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:39.54,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Apparently, they leaked information about Oryo to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.96,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.10,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,But what's their motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:46.75,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,They might have thought that\Nthe closing of the amakudari loophole
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:50.13,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,was an opportune moment to crush Yakushiji Ryoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.55,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,"Serves her right,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:56.26,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,is what I'd like to say, but we can't say that in a very nice way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.81,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,If they're going to crush Oryo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:01.65,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,they should lower the iron hammer in the name of the law, fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.68,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Not by using the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.73,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Superintendent Muromachi, they just keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.61,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,We need more guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.63,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.91,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,You came at the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.12,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,You're the one who came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.58,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Please hold a press meeting as Oryo's direct subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:22.58,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,If you do, I'm sure everyone will be content and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:23.39,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.06,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,No, I can't hold a press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.09,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,You just need to say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.55,Ryōko main,Kis,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.19,Ryōko main,Yuk,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Kishimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.81,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,It's Lieutenant Izumida!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.22,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.51,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:35.51,Ryōko overlap,Jun,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.90,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.14,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Where is Yakushiji Ryoko right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.10,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Is it true that she fled?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.36,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,What is your relation with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.06,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,Please answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.07,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.12,Ryōko main,Man,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.05,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.01,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.48,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:32.56,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Her expression was unquestionably different from ten days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.70,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,Could it be due to the Amakudari Regulation Bill and the stinging broadcasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:41.46,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,No, she's looking at something... completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.17,Ryōko italic,Jun,0,0,0,,That is what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:44.39,Ryōko main,Lue,0,0,0,,Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.14,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Why are you giving me something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.52,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,It's to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.68,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,Please take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.97,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.52,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,You'll know when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.28,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.08,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,You'll know when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.39,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,And take this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.60,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:10.03,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,It's a card key I've created using the data\Ncollected from the Japanese Private Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.87,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,With this, all NPP keys are good for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.95,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Why are you giving me something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.41,Ryōko main,Non,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:22.03,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,I'll know when I get there, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:06.71,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.56,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.23,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.27,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.45,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,That's the security robot for nuclear power plants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.66,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,They even have those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:42.16,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What exactly is stored here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:46.02,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx100\pos(320,478)}Marianne, Lucienne, can you play with the dangerous kid there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:49.39,Ryōko main,Two,0,0,0,,{\be1\3a&H30&\fscx110\pos(320,478)}Yes, Mistress, leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.67,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.14,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,S-Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:06.98,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.90,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,Ryoko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.99,Ryōko main,Lad,0,0,0,,it's so like you... to come barging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:32.37,Ryōko italic,Ryo,0,0,0,,I won't let you have your way, Queen of Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.79,Ryōko italic,Ryo,0,0,0,,Isurugi Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.19,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.44,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:02.45,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm still... alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.17,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.21,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,She looks identical to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.58,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:22.99,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.52,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why is she a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.31,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,What were you like when you were little, Superintendent?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:19.44,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,The same as I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:23.43,Ryōko main,Ryo,0,0,0,,Beautiful, pure, kindhearted, completely innocent, and loved by everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:25.22,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Yakushiji Ryoko's Supernatural Case File,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:26.68,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,File Number 09-B:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.51,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Trap in Azabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:28.64,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:29.22,Ryōko main,Jun,0,0,0,,And umm...
